{"lemma":"تَمَكُّنٌ","slug":"تَمَكُّنٌ","root":"م.ك.ن","root_slug":"م-ك-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/م-ك-ن","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":5,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n43667"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AA%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%8E%D9%83%D9%8F%D9%91%D9%86%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be influential"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be able to, to be in the position to","examples":[{"text":"ويشار بحسب المجلة، بان اعداد إرهابيي داعش الأجانب ما زال كبيرا جدا على الرغم من التقديرات التي ترجح مقتل الآلاف منهم، حيث تظهر البيانات المجموعة من 33 دولة لها مواطنين يقاتلون مع عصابات داعش الإرهابية، ان ما يزيد عن 6000 منهم قد تمكنوا من العودة الى بلدانهم، فيما تصل اعداد الغائبين إلى الآلاف المضاعفة.","english":"It is shown by the magazine that the number of foreign ISIS terrorists has not ceased to be very large in spite of assessments that affirm the death of thousands of them as likely, whereas the data gathered from 33 states to which citizens fighting for terrorist ISIS groups belong reveals that more than 6000 of them have had the opportunity of returning to their homelands, while the number of absentees has reached several thousands."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to master, to take the power over"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"power, might; capability, ability"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"power, might; control, mastery"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n43667","headword_ar":"تَمَكَّنَ","root":"mkn","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aisotaqar~a","text_ar":"اِسْتَقَرَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qr","text_ar":"قر"},{"kind":"text","text":":) it is very often used in this sense, as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, settled; became fixed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"established; it became fixed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"steady, in its place;"},{"kind":"text","text":"when said of a man, particularly implying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in authority and power:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qar~a","text_ar":"قَرَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tamak~ana mino $aYo'K","text_ar":"تَمَكَّنَ مِنْ شَىْءٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aisotamokana","text_ar":"اِسْتَمْكَنَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He became possessed of mastery,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dominion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ascendancy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"authority, and power, over a thing; he was able to avail himself of it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, within reach of him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it."},{"kind":"text","text":"] (Msb.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tamak~ana minohu","text_ar":"تَمَكَّنَ مِنْهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He assumed authority over him."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}